      <![CDATA[<h1 id="太赫兹-CSAR-20-16GHz-多基线三维成像实验方案"><a href="#太赫兹-CSAR-20-16GHz-多基线三维成像实验方案" class="headerlink" title="太赫兹 CSAR 20.16GHz 多基线三维成像实验方案"></a>太赫兹 CSAR 20.16GHz 多基线三维成像实验方案</h1><p>本文根据当前实验硬件条件整理了一套可直接执行的太赫兹暗室实验流程：中心频率 <span class="math-inline">&#92;(213.84\text{ GHz}&#92;)</span>、扫频带宽 <span class="math-inline">&#92;(20.16\text{ GHz}&#92;)</span>、恒速自旋转台 <span class="math-inline">&#92;(4^\circ&#x2F;\text{s}&#92;)</span>、单圈 90 秒、手动计时控制、转台旋转后需手动复位。</p><p>目标是让实验流程更规范，并通过后处理算法消除手动对齐带来的时间差，顺利运行 <code>code</code> 文件夹下的三维层析成像（Tomo-CSAR）算法。</p><h2 id="一、核心物理参数核算与实验设计"><a href="#一、核心物理参数核算与实验设计" class="headerlink" title="一、核心物理参数核算与实验设计"></a>一、核心物理参数核算与实验设计</h2><p>在太赫兹频段，波长极短，微小的位置误差都会明显影响相位，因此先给出系统的关键参数。</p><h3 id="1-雷达与电磁波基础参数"><a href="#1-雷达与电磁波基础参数" class="headerlink" title="1. 雷达与电磁波基础参数"></a>1. 雷达与电磁波基础参数</h3><ul><li>中心频率 <span class="math-inline">&#92;(f_c &#x3D; 213.84\text{ GHz}&#92;)</span>。</li><li>扫频带宽 <span class="math-inline">&#92;(B &#x3D; 20.16\text{ GHz}&#92;)</span>。</li><li>扫频范围为 <span class="math-inline">&#92;(203.76\text{ GHz} \sim 223.92\text{ GHz}&#92;)</span>。</li><li>工作波长 <span class="math-inline">&#92;(\lambda &#x3D; \frac{c}{f_c} \approx \textbf{1.402 mm}&#92;)</span>。</li></ul><p>距离向物理分辨率为：</p><div class="math-display">&#92;[\rho_r = \frac{c}{2B} = \frac{299792458}{2 \times 20.16\text{e}9} \approx \textbf{7.43 mm}&#92;]</div><p>这意味着系统具有很高的距离向分辨能力，适合提取精细的三维散射中心。</p><h3 id="2-多基线空间几何设计"><a href="#2-多基线空间几何设计" class="headerlink" title="2. 多基线空间几何设计"></a>2. 多基线空间几何设计</h3><p>根据目标距离 <span class="math-inline">&#92;(R &#x3D; 4.0\text{ m}&#92;)</span>、俯仰角 <span class="math-inline">&#92;(\theta_{el} \approx 10^\circ&#92;)</span> 进行设计。</p><p>为了保证最大高度为 <span class="math-inline">&#92;(30\text{ cm}&#92;)</span> 的靶标在成像时不产生高度向折叠，设定垂直基线步进 <span class="math-inline">&#92;(\Delta z &#x3D; 8\text{ mm}&#92;)</span>。理论最大无模糊高度为：</p><div class="math-display">&#92;[H_{amb} = \frac{\lambda R}{2 \Delta z \cos(\theta_{el})}= \frac{1.402\text{ mm} \times 4000\text{ mm}}{2 \times 8\text{ mm} \times \cos(10^\circ)}\approx \textbf{35.59 cm} &gt; 30\text{ cm}&#92;]</div><p>设定基线总数 <span class="math-inline">&#92;(M &#x3D; 11&#92;)</span>，垂直升降架总位移行程 <span class="math-inline">&#92;(L &#x3D; (M - 1) \cdot \Delta z &#x3D; 80\text{ mm}&#92;)</span>。则高度维分辨率为：</p><div class="math-display">&#92;[\rho_z \approx \frac{\lambda R}{2 L \cos(\theta_{el})}= \frac{1.402\text{ mm} \times 4000\text{ mm}}{2 \times 80\text{ mm} \times \cos(10^\circ)}\approx \textbf{3.56 cm}&#92;]</div><h2 id="二、实验室标准化“手动变轨-时序”工作流"><a href="#二、实验室标准化“手动变轨-时序”工作流" class="headerlink" title="二、实验室标准化“手动变轨-时序”工作流"></a>二、实验室标准化“手动变轨-时序”工作流</h2><p>由于硬件没有自动联动机制，每完成一轨（1 圈扫描）后，都需要手动将目标复位到 <span class="math-inline">&#92;(0^\circ&#92;)</span> 起始位置，再升高雷达高度。下面给出标准化时序流程。</p><h3 id="单轨循环时序"><a href="#单轨循环时序" class="headerlink" title="单轨循环时序"></a>单轨循环时序</h3><ol><li><p>准备工作：在转台边缘和静止底座上贴一对高精度物理刻度线，作为 <span class="math-inline">&#92;(0^\circ&#92;)</span> 的绝对参考基准。</p></li><li><p>手动复位：转动转盘，使目标回到起始位置，令转台刻度线与底座刻度线严格对齐。</p></li><li><p>变高调整：通过步进电机将雷达高度调整到指定位置：</p><div class="math-display">&#92;[Z_{ib} = H_{base} + (ib - 1) \times 8\text{ mm}&#92;]</div></li><li><p>启动转盘：使目标开始以 <span class="math-inline">&#92;(4^\circ&#x2F;\text{s}&#92;)</span> 匀速旋转。</p></li><li><p>启动采集：关注刻度线。当发现刻度线开始错开、代表转盘刚开始转动时，立即在电脑端触发 VNA 开始计时录取。</p></li><li><p>计时录取：VNA 连续扫频录取，数据持续 90 秒，此时转盘刚好完成 360° 旋转。</p></li><li><p>保存归档：90 秒到后停止录取，将当前圈数据保存为 <code>pass[ib].mat</code>。</p></li><li><p>关停转盘：关闭转盘电源，准备进入下一轨。</p></li></ol><h3 id="VNA-关键设置"><a href="#VNA-关键设置" class="headerlink" title="VNA 关键设置"></a>VNA 关键设置</h3><ul><li>扫频范围：<span class="math-inline">&#92;(203.76\text{ GHz} \sim 223.92\text{ GHz}&#92;)</span>。</li><li>频点数：<span class="math-inline">&#92;(N_r &#x3D; 512&#92;)</span>，不要设得过高，以兼顾成像速度。</li><li>中频带宽（IFBW）：建议设为 <span class="math-inline">&#92;(20\text{ kHz}&#92;)</span>。</li><li>单次扫频加数据回传时间约为 <span class="math-inline">&#92;(100\text{ ms}&#92;)</span>。</li></ul><p>在 90 秒内可以稳定采集到：</p><div class="math-display">&#92;[N_a = 90 / 0.1 = 900&#92;]</div><p>对应的等效方位角间隔为：</p><div class="math-display">&#92;[\Delta \theta = 360^\circ / 900 = 0.4^\circ&#92;]</div><p>这足以避免太赫兹频段的方位向空域混叠。</p><h2 id="三、起始角自动平移对齐与格式转换脚本"><a href="#三、起始角自动平移对齐与格式转换脚本" class="headerlink" title="三、起始角自动平移对齐与格式转换脚本"></a>三、起始角自动平移对齐与格式转换脚本</h2><p>由于采集由手动计时启动，各轨开始录取的时刻不可避免会存在数十毫秒、约等效于 <span class="math-inline">&#92;(1^\circ \sim 3^\circ&#92;)</span> 的时间差，容易导致 11 幅二维 SLC 图像在高度向干涉时散焦。</p><p>下面的 MATLAB 脚本针对 <span class="math-inline">&#92;(20.16\text{ GHz}&#92;)</span> 带宽系统编写。它读取 11 个原始 <code>passX.mat</code> 文件，在复数回波域中执行一维距离像变换，找到散射最强的时刻，再利用 <code>circshift</code> 自动将 11 条基线的方位角圆周平移对齐，并封装为 GOTCHA 规范格式。</p><figure class="highlight matlab"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br><span class="line">68</span><br><span class="line">69</span><br><span class="line">70</span><br><span class="line">71</span><br><span class="line">72</span><br><span class="line">73</span><br><span class="line">74</span><br><span class="line">75</span><br><span class="line">76</span><br><span class="line">77</span><br><span class="line">78</span><br><span class="line">79</span><br><span class="line">80</span><br><span class="line">81</span><br><span class="line">82</span><br><span class="line">83</span><br><span class="line">84</span><br><span class="line">85</span><br><span class="line">86</span><br><span class="line">87</span><br><span class="line">88</span><br><span class="line">89</span><br><span class="line">90</span><br><span class="line">91</span><br><span class="line">92</span><br><span class="line">93</span><br><span class="line">94</span><br><span class="line">95</span><br><span class="line">96</span><br><span class="line">97</span><br><span class="line">98</span><br><span class="line">99</span><br><span class="line">100</span><br><span class="line">101</span><br><span class="line">102</span><br><span class="line">103</span><br><span class="line">104</span><br><span class="line">105</span><br><span class="line">106</span><br><span class="line">107</span><br><span class="line">108</span><br><span class="line">109</span><br><span class="line">110</span><br><span class="line">111</span><br><span class="line">112</span><br><span class="line">113</span><br><span class="line">114</span><br><span class="line">115</span><br><span class="line">116</span><br><span class="line">117</span><br><span class="line">118</span><br><span class="line">119</span><br><span class="line">120</span><br><span class="line">121</span><br><span class="line">122</span><br><span class="line">123</span><br><span class="line">124</span><br><span class="line">125</span><br><span class="line">126</span><br><span class="line">127</span><br><span class="line">128</span><br><span class="line">129</span><br><span class="line">130</span><br><span class="line">131</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">% =========================================================================</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">% THz_CSAR_20G_Packager_SelfAligned.m</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">% 作用：将 20.16GHz 太赫兹 CSAR 手动时序采集数据封装成 GOTCHA 标准格式，</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">%       并利用最强散射中心角度实现 11 轨方位角自动精确平移对齐。</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">% =========================================================================</span></span><br><span class="line">clear; clc;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">%% 1. 20.16GHz 太赫兹系统与几何参数</span></span><br><span class="line">c = <span class="number">299792458</span>;</span><br><span class="line">fc = <span class="number">213.84e9</span>;                          <span class="comment">% 中心频率 (213.84 GHz)</span></span><br><span class="line">B = <span class="number">20.16e9</span>;                            <span class="comment">% 扫频带宽 (20.16 GHz)</span></span><br><span class="line">Nb = <span class="number">11</span>;                                <span class="comment">% 基线数</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">R = <span class="number">4.0</span>;                                <span class="comment">% 靶标到天线相位中心的平均斜距 (m)</span></span><br><span class="line">theta_el = <span class="number">10</span>;                          <span class="comment">% 俯仰角 (度)</span></span><br><span class="line">Baseline_step = <span class="number">0.008</span>;                  <span class="comment">% 垂直基线间隔 (8 mm)</span></span><br><span class="line">H_base = R * <span class="built_in">sin</span>(deg2rad(theta_el));    <span class="comment">% 第一条基线高度</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">out_dir = <span class="string">&#x27;../mergeData&#x27;</span>;               <span class="comment">% tomo_z.m 加载路径</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> ~exist(out_dir, <span class="string">&#x27;dir&#x27;</span>), mkdir(out_dir); <span class="keyword">end</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">%% 2. 预读并自动计算各轨的起始角度移位量</span></span><br><span class="line">fprintf(<span class="string">&#x27;========== 第一阶段：分析 11 轨起始角偏差 ==========&#x27;</span>\n);</span><br><span class="line">raw_cells = cell(<span class="number">1</span>, Nb);</span><br><span class="line">peak_pulse_indices = <span class="built_in">zeros</span>(<span class="number">1</span>, Nb);      <span class="comment">% 记录每轨最强反射峰值出现的脉冲序号</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> ib = <span class="number">1</span> : Nb</span><br><span class="line">    raw_file = sprintf(<span class="string">&#x27;pass%d.mat&#x27;</span>, ib);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> ~exist(raw_file, <span class="string">&#x27;file&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        error(<span class="string">&#x27;未找到原始文件: %s，请检查路径！&#x27;</span>, raw_file);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">end</span></span><br><span class="line">    tmp = load(raw_file); <span class="comment">% 载入后变量为 raw_echo</span></span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">% 转换尺寸为 [Nr x Na] (第一维距离向，第二维方位向)</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> <span class="built_in">size</span>(tmp.raw_echo, <span class="number">1</span>) == <span class="number">512</span></span><br><span class="line">        raw_cells&#123;ib&#125; = tmp.raw_echo;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">        raw_cells&#123;ib&#125; = tmp.raw_echo.&#x27;; </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">end</span></span><br><span class="line">    [Nr_tmp, Na_tmp] = <span class="built_in">size</span>(raw_cells&#123;ib&#125;);</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">% 核心自聚焦：沿着距离向做一维 FFT 寻找最强反射脉冲</span></span><br><span class="line">    Nfft = <span class="number">1024</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    rc_all = fftshift(fft(raw_cells&#123;ib&#125;, Nfft, <span class="number">1</span>), <span class="number">1</span>); </span><br><span class="line">    rc_amp = <span class="built_in">abs</span>(rc_all);</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    [pulse_max_val, ~] = <span class="built_in">max</span>(rc_amp, [], <span class="number">1</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    [~, max_pulse_idx] = <span class="built_in">max</span>(pulse_max_val);</span><br><span class="line">    peak_pulse_indices(ib) = max_pulse_idx;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    fprintf(<span class="string">&#x27;基线 %d/%d：脉冲总数 %d，最强散射峰值出现在第 %d 个脉冲。\n&#x27;</span>, ...</span><br><span class="line">        ib, Nb, Na_tmp, max_pulse_idx);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">end</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">% 以第 1 轨为绝对基准角，计算其余各轨对应的平移量</span></span><br><span class="line">target_align_idx = peak_pulse_indices(<span class="number">1</span>);</span><br><span class="line">fprintf(<span class="string">&#x27;&gt;&gt;&gt; 选定对齐基准脉冲序号为: %d\n\n&#x27;</span>, target_align_idx);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">%% 3. 执行角度自动对准与 GOTCHA 标准结构体打包</span></span><br><span class="line">fprintf(<span class="string">&#x27;========== 第二阶段：执行移位平移并封装打包 ==========&#x27;</span>\n);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> ib = <span class="number">1</span> : Nb</span><br><span class="line">    raw_echo_aligned = raw_cells&#123;ib&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">    [Nr, Na] = <span class="built_in">size</span>(raw_echo_aligned);</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">% 计算循环移位量 (circshift 使得方位维圆周对准)</span></span><br><span class="line">    shift_amount = target_align_idx - peak_pulse_indices(ib);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> shift_amount ~= <span class="number">0</span></span><br><span class="line">        raw_echo_aligned = <span class="built_in">circshift</span>(raw_echo_aligned, shift_amount, <span class="number">2</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        fprintf(<span class="string">&#x27;基线 %d 已成功对齐，平移修正量: %+d 个脉冲。\n&#x27;</span>, ib, shift_amount);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">        fprintf(<span class="string">&#x27;基线 %d 无起始偏差，保持基准对齐。\n&#x27;</span>, ib);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">end</span></span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">% --- 开始伪装并构建 GOTCHA 规范结构体 ---</span></span><br><span class="line">    data = struct();</span><br><span class="line">    data.phdata = raw_echo_aligned;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">% A. 构造频率轴</span></span><br><span class="line">    f_start = fc - B/<span class="number">2</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    f_end = fc + B/<span class="number">2</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    data.freq = <span class="built_in">linspace</span>(f_start, f_end, Nr).&#x27;; <span class="comment">% 必须为 [Nr x 1] 的列向量</span></span><br><span class="line">    data.deltaF = diff(data.freq(<span class="number">1</span>:<span class="number">2</span>));</span><br><span class="line">    data.minF = <span class="built_in">min</span>(data.freq) * <span class="built_in">ones</span>(<span class="number">1</span>, Na);   <span class="comment">% [1 x Na]</span></span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">% B. 构造 CSAR 轨迹空间坐标 (等效雷达绕飞模型)</span></span><br><span class="line">    data.th = <span class="built_in">linspace</span>(<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">360</span>, Na);             <span class="comment">% 0~360度方位角</span></span><br><span class="line">    theta_rad = deg2rad(data.th);</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    R_xy = R * <span class="built_in">cos</span>(deg2rad(theta_el));          <span class="comment">% 水平旋转半径</span></span><br><span class="line">    data.AntX = R_xy * <span class="built_in">cos</span>(theta_rad);          <span class="comment">% [1 x Na] 行向量</span></span><br><span class="line">    data.AntY = -R_xy * <span class="built_in">sin</span>(theta_rad);         <span class="comment">% 负号对应转盘逆时针旋转</span></span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">% 计算高度变轨轨迹 Z</span></span><br><span class="line">    current_height = H_base + (ib - <span class="number">1</span>) * Baseline_step;</span><br><span class="line">    data.AntZ = current_height * <span class="built_in">ones</span>(<span class="number">1</span>, Na);   <span class="comment">% [1 x Na]</span></span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">% C. 几何辅助与斜距计算</span></span><br><span class="line">    data.r0 = <span class="built_in">sqrt</span>(data.AntX.^<span class="number">2</span> + data.AntY.^<span class="number">2</span> + data.AntZ.^<span class="number">2</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    data.phi = atan2d(data.AntZ, <span class="built_in">sqrt</span>(data.AntX.^<span class="number">2</span> + data.AntY.^<span class="number">2</span>)); <span class="comment">% 仰角</span></span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">% D. 矫正项初始化为零 (后续使用自聚焦 af_flag=1 处理微小波动)</span></span><br><span class="line">    data.r_correct = <span class="built_in">zeros</span>(<span class="number">1</span>, Na);</span><br><span class="line">    data.ph_correct = <span class="built_in">zeros</span>(<span class="number">1</span>, Na);</span><br><span class="line">    data.Nfft = <span class="number">8192</span>;                           </span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">% E. 构造 GOTCHA 索引映射表 Npulse (extractSubapData 核心依赖)</span></span><br><span class="line">    data.Npulse = <span class="built_in">zeros</span>(<span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">360</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> deg = <span class="number">1</span> : <span class="number">360</span></span><br><span class="line">        mask = (data.th &gt;= (deg<span class="number">-1</span>) &amp; data.th &lt; deg);</span><br><span class="line">        idx = <span class="built_in">find</span>(mask);</span><br><span class="line">        </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> ~<span class="built_in">isempty</span>(idx)</span><br><span class="line">            data.Npulse(<span class="number">1</span>, deg) = <span class="built_in">length</span>(idx);   </span><br><span class="line">            data.Npulse(<span class="number">2</span>, deg) = idx(<span class="number">1</span>);        </span><br><span class="line">            data.Npulse(<span class="number">3</span>, deg) = idx(<span class="keyword">end</span>);      </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> deg &gt; <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">                data.Npulse(<span class="number">2</span>:<span class="number">3</span>, deg) = data.Npulse(<span class="number">3</span>, deg<span class="number">-1</span>);</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">                data.Npulse(<span class="number">2</span>:<span class="number">3</span>, deg) = <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">end</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">end</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">end</span></span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">% 保存符合 tomo_z.m 加载规则的数据</span></span><br><span class="line">    save_name = sprintf(<span class="string">&#x27;%s/pass%d_HH.mat&#x27;</span>, out_dir, ib);</span><br><span class="line">    save(save_name, <span class="string">&#x27;data&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;-v7.3&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">end</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">fprintf(<span class="string">&#x27;\n🎉 恭喜！数据打包对准全部成功。文件已保存在 %s 文件夹中。\n&#x27;</span>, out_dir);</span><br><span class="line">fprintf(<span class="string">&#x27;现在您可以直接运行 tomo_z.m (设置 Nb=11) 来运行层析聚焦算法！\n&#x27;</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="四、20-16GHz-220GHz-暗室实验三大避坑指南"><a href="#四、20-16GHz-220GHz-暗室实验三大避坑指南" class="headerlink" title="四、20.16GHz &#x2F; 220GHz 暗室实验三大避坑指南"></a>四、20.16GHz &#x2F; 220GHz 暗室实验三大避坑指南</h2><h3 id="1-极敏感相位与微小抖动"><a href="#1-极敏感相位与微小抖动" class="headerlink" title="1. 极敏感相位与微小抖动"></a>1. 极敏感相位与微小抖动</h3><p>在 220GHz 下，波长只有约 <span class="math-inline">&#92;(1.4\text{ mm}&#92;)</span>。调整雷达高度或复位目标时，连接雷达射频源与 VNA 的高频柔性线缆会产生轻微扭曲，进而带来几十微米级别的波程偏差，形成明显的随机相位误差。</p><p>建议：在成像代码中不要直接使用未经相位校准的结果。在 <code>tomo_z.m</code> 中务必设置 <code>af_flag = 1</code>，开启自聚焦算法（PGA &#x2F; 最小熵法），这是保证实测层析像稳定成形的关键。</p><h3 id="2-计时启动的物理参考散射点"><a href="#2-计时启动的物理参考散射点" class="headerlink" title="2. 计时启动的物理参考散射点"></a>2. 计时启动的物理参考散射点</h3><p>为了让“自动角度对齐”算法生效，需要让靶标在某个旋转角具有非常强的反射能量。</p><p>建议：在转盘边缘或者靶标本身的特定方向贴一个角反射器，或者高反射率金属条，作为“相位对齐标记”。只要每一轨这个强反光标不发生位移，该算法对齐精度可达到约 <span class="math-inline">&#92;(0.1^\circ&#92;)</span>，明显优于手动计时精度。</p><h3 id="3-转台转速稳定度核查"><a href="#3-转台转速稳定度核查" class="headerlink" title="3. 转台转速稳定度核查"></a>3. 转台转速稳定度核查</h3><p>由于转台以 <span class="math-inline">&#92;(4^\circ&#x2F;\text{s}&#92;)</span> 恒速旋转，如果启动瞬间存在“先慢后快”的缓冲过程，就会导致方位角与时间的线性映射不准。</p><p>建议：在执行第 4 步触发采集时，尽量等转盘转速完全进入稳定匀速状态后再按下采集键。例如可以在启动转台 2 秒、速度均匀后再开始计时录取，此时手动复位线应提前逆时针偏置约 8° 作为预留量。</p>]]>
